ngs), 1255; 1 pm - 7 pm: The Bone Connection  an exhibition of sculptures and installations by Prasun Ghosh.     Till April 22 (except Sunday) at Aakriti Art Gallery, 12/3A Hungerford Street, 3027/ 5041; 12 noon - 7 pm: Image and Symbol, an exhibition of paintings and sculptures by renowned artists.     Till April 23 at Chitrakoot Art Gallery, 55 Gariahat Road, 2275; 3 pm - 8 pm: An exhibition of recent paintings by Shyam Sharma     Till April 25 at Taj Bengal (By the Way); 11 am - 7 pm: Paintings by Ranadip Das.     Till April 30 (except Sundays) at Ganges Art Gallery, 33A Jatin Das Road, 11 am - 7 pm: Within the Grid, a solo exhibition of Avijit Mukherjees work.     Till April 30 (Sundays by appointment) at Idiyas Gallery, 15 Dover Road, -05003, 65508418; 10.30 am - 6.30 pm: The Voices of the Canvas, featuring works by Prokash Karmakar, Ramananda Bandyopadhyay, Suhas Roy, Bratin Khan, Subrata Das, Shyamal Mukherjee, Sukanta Das, Samir Paul, Atin Basak and others.     
